'''病毒血症'''（英文：Viremia）是指[[病毒|病毒]]侵入[[血液|血液]]系统的状况，病毒可由此进入身体其它部分。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Viremia - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/viremia|accessdate=2021-04-01|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020233724/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/viremia|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Definition of Viremia|url=https://www.medicinenet.com/viremia/definition.htm|accessdate=2021-04-01|work=MedicineNet|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421043624/https://www.medicinenet.com/viremia/definition.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 病毒血症与[[菌血症|菌血症]]相似，后者指[[细菌|细菌]]侵入血液。<ref name=":0" />

== 阶段 ==
初期病毒血症指的是病毒从最初感染点开始在血液中的扩散，一般持续4-5天；二期病毒血症指的是病毒通过血液系统感染了其它[[组织_(生物学)|组织]]，此期间病毒（在新感染[[细胞|细胞]]内）已经进行了{{le|病毒复制|Viral replication}}并再次进入血液循环。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mechanisms of Infection and Spread of Viruses through the Body|url=http://csmbio.csm.jmu.edu/biology/virology/Viral%20Spread/spread.html|accessdate=2021-04-01|work=|publisher=[[詹姆斯·麦迪逊大学|詹姆斯·麦迪逊大学]]|language=en|archive-date=2016-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708082149/http://csmbio.csm.jmu.edu/biology/virology/Viral%20Spread/spread.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 通常情况下，二期病毒血症会有更大量的{{le|病毒排出|Viral shedding}}、[[病毒载量|病毒载量]]，这是因为病毒利用血液系统能找到自然宿主细胞，从而进行更高效地复制（相比在最初感染点）。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Antibody responses to the hepatitis C virus E2 protein: relationship to viraemia and prevalence in anti-HCV seronegative subjects|date=Jan 1997|journal=J Med Virol|issue=1|doi=10.1002/(sici)1096-9071(199701)51:1<1::aid-jmv1>3.3.co;2-3|volume=51|pages=1–5|pmid=8986942|vauthors=Cerino A, Bissolati M, Cividini A, Nicosia A, Esumi M, Hayashi N, Mizuno K, Slobbe R, Oudshoorn P, Silini E, Asti M, Mondelli MU}}</ref>

最典型的例子之一就是[[狂犬病病毒|狂犬病病毒]]，该病毒在最初感染点（如动物咬伤的肌肉处）可进行简短的复制，并引发初期病毒血症，此后病毒会散播到中枢神经系统、引发二期病毒血症，而患者也开始出现狂犬病症状。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Viral RNA in the bloodstream suggests viremia occurs in clinically ill rabies-infected mice|url=https://zenodo.org/record/1259445|date=Mar 2006|journal=Virus Res.|issue=1–2|doi=10.1016/j.virusres.2005.09.004|volume=116|pages=114–8|type=Submitted manuscript|pmid=16242805|vauthors=Lodmell DL, Dimcheff DE, Ewalt LC|access-date=2021-04-01|archive-date=2020-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709044315/https://zenodo.org/record/1259445|dead-url=no}}</ref> 当到了二期病毒血症时，接种[[狂犬病疫苗|狂犬病疫苗]]已经无效，病毒侵入[[大脑|大脑]]已无法被阻止。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Viraemia in rabies|date=Jul 1982|journal=Acta Virol|issue=4|volume=26|page=301|vauthors=Gribencha SV, Barinsky IF}}</ref> 因此，接种疫苗必须在二期病毒血症之前。

== 机制 ==
主动型病毒血症是由于病毒的主动复制而导致病毒进入血液，典型的例子包括[[麻疹病毒|麻疹病毒]]。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Antigen-Specific B-Cell Responses to Porcine Reproductive and Respiratory Syndrome Virus Infection|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2224379/|last=Mulupuri|first=Prasad|last2=Zimmerman|first2=Jeffrey J.|date=2008-1|journal=Journal of Virology|issue=1|doi=10.1128/JVI.01023-07|volume=82|pages=358–370|issn=0022-538X|pmc=2224379|pmid=17942527|last3=Hermann|first3=Joseph|last4=Johnson|first4=Craig R.|last5=Cano|first5=Jean Paul|last6=Yu|first6=Wanqin|last7=Dee|first7=Scott A.|last8=Murtaugh|first8=Michael P.}}</ref> 而被动型病毒血症则无需病毒主动复制，典型例子包括蚊虫叮咬、[[输血|输血]]、物理伤害等导致病毒直接进入血液。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Epitope determinants of a chimpanzee dengue virus type 4 (DENV-4)-neutralizing antibody and protection against DENV-4 challenge in mice and rhesus monkeys by passively transferred humanized antibody|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-virology_2007-12_81_23/page/12766|date=Dec 2007|journal=J Virol|issue=23|doi=10.1128/jvi.01420-07|volume=81|pages=12766–74|pmc=2169078|pmid=17881450|vauthors=Lai CJ, Goncalvez AP, Men R, Wernly C, Donau O, Engle RE, Purcell RH}}</ref>

